   <dc:title>Handwritten postcard from Frimmel to Schenker, dated March 14, 1905</dc:title>

   <dcterms:created>1905-03-14T12:00:00Z</dcterms:created>
   <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2020-07-22</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
   <dc:description>The promised Handel Organ Concertos volume has not yet arrived. — Frimmel asks
    for the score of the C. P. E. Bach concerto that Schenker played the previous fall. Tickets for
    his Beethoven lectures will be sent soon.</dc:description>
